metadata.name: Meeting God
metadata.description:
I'm a Barbie girl, in a Barbie world
Life in plastic, it's fantastic
You can brush my hair, undress me everywhere
Imagination, life is your creation

A combination of ethereal settings, with unnerving characters swallow you in my DREAMWORLDS series. Originally created as a form of escapism from my depression, these digital paintings have become a representation of what it feels like to dream, and live, with a mental health condition.
